Nightmare mudlib room lfun: set_exits()

void set_exits(string *dests, string *dirs)

Creates an exit leading to each member of "dests" activated by the verbs in 
"dirs".  "dests" and "dirs" must both be arrays of the same size.  "dests" 
should be an array of filenames to the rooms desired and "dirs" should be an 
array of verbs or directions to get to the desired rooms.

See also: add_exit(), remove_exit()
Defined in /std/room/exits.c
